<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Our History</title>

  <!-- Tipografías elegantes -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600&family=Open+Sans&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

</head>
<body>

  <div id="nosotros"></div>
  <section class="seccion-historia">
    <div class="historia-contenido">
      
      <div class="historia-imagenes">
        <img src="antigua.jpeg" alt="Old bakery photo">
      </div>

      <div class="historia-texto">
        <h2>Our History</h2>
        <p>
          At <strong>El Rincón del Repostero</strong>, our story begins with a lit oven and a clear vision: to elevate the art of baking. We were born from a love of authentic flavors, delicate aesthetics, and time-honored tradition.
          <br><br>
          Since our inception, we've blended classic techniques with a modern twist. Each recipe is a chapter, each cake an emotion. More than products, we create experiences that shape celebrations, moments, and memories.
          <br><br>
          Today, we continue baking with the same love that started it all — knowing every dessert holds a story worth telling.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      background-color: #fffaf7;
      color: #3b2e25;
    }

    .seccion-historia {
      padding: 100px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fffaf7 0%, #f3e9df 100%);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .historia-contenido {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 60px;
      background-color: #eaddcf;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 50px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      max-width: 1200px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
    }

    .historia-imagenes {
      flex: 1 1 450px;
      animation: fadeInLeft 1s ease;
    }

    .historia-imagenes img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
      animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    }

    .historia-imagenes img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.04);
    }

    .historia-texto {
      flex: 1 1 500px;
    }

    .historia-texto h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      color: #3b2e25;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      position: relative;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .historia-texto h2::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -10px;
      left: 0;
      width: 60px;
      height: 4px;
      background-color: #c79d5e;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .historia-texto p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: #4c4038;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .historia-contenido {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px;
      }

      .historia-texto h2::after {
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
      }
    }

    /* Animaciones */
    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(40px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInLeft {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-50px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
